response.overview: Contemporary gospel supergroup Tye Tribbett & G.A. took to the stage of a Philadelphia megachurch to record the follow-up, Victory Live!, thus offering a more true-to-form representation of the group's sound, synergy, and spirit. Victory Live! is an of the moment take on Tye Tribbett's musical journey that has become his trademark. Its cinematic spiritual storytelling based the travels trials and tribulations of Tye's life.
response.title: Victory Live! Tye Tribbett
